cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.CL

The paper deals with automatic generation of video summaries of TV series using social network analysis and filmmaking grammar. This involves modeling the dynamics of the plot and extracting relevant sequences. The paper also carries out evaluation with a user study. Based on this, the most likely sub-category is cs.MM (Multimedia), followed by cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CV (Computer Vision), and cs.CL (Computation and Language).
